title: ‘Survivor,’ Season 42, Episode 8 With Jeremy Collins
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by 'Survivor: Cambodia' winner Jeremy Collins to discuss the latest episode of ‘Survivor.’ They get into the results of the immunity challenge, the double tribal council, and as always, give out some superlatives. Plus, they discuss an emotional moment bigger than the game.

Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Jeremy Collins
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
